Steps to compile:

1. Clone ITensor and switch to rc3 branch:
     cd the/folder/where/you/want/itensor/
     git clone https://github.com/ITensor/ITensor.git itensor
     git checkout rc3

2. Set up and compile ITensor:
     cp options.mk.sample options.mk
     <then edit options.mk and adjust to your computer's settings>
     make

3. Set up a Makefile for yourself:
     cp Makefile.miles Makefile.myname
     ln -s Makefile.myname Makefile
     <then edit the top line of Makefile.myname to point to where ITensor is installed>

4. Compile the learn.cc program:
     make
